==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|ki}}

===Etymology===
Derived from ''[[kirja]]'', which originally meant "drawn decorative pattern" [1], with the suffix ''[[-e]]''.

===Noun===
'''kirje'''

# [[letter]] (a written message).

